### Health Check - Issuance Service
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

### Health Check - Verification Service
GET http://localhost:3002/api/health

### Issue a new credential
POST http://localhost:3001/api/issue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "CRED-1704892800000-TEST123",
  "holderName": "Alice Johnson",
  "holderEmail": "alice.johnson@example.com",
  "credentialType": "Academic Certificate",
  "issueDate": "2025-01-10T10:00:00.000Z",
  "expiryDate": "2026-01-10T10:00:00.000Z",
  "metadata": {
    "university": "MIT",
    "degree": "Bachelor of Science"
  }
}

### Get credential by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/credentials/CRED-1704892800000-TEST123

### Get all credentials
GET http://localhost:3001/api/credentials

### Verify valid credential
POST http://localhost:3002/api/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "CRED-1704892800000-TEST123"
}

### Verify invalid credential
POST http://localhost:3002/api/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "INVALID-CREDENTIAL-ID"
}

### Get verification logs
GET http://localhost:3002/api/logs

### Get logs for specific credential
GET http://localhost:3002/api/logs?credentialId=CRED-1704892800000-TEST123
